Ready to shop smarter? 🛒✨ Here are my top 5 items I skip for a healthier cart: 

1. Vegetable oils (hello ghee & olive oil!) 
2. Table sugar (dates are my jam!) 
3. Snacks (nuts are my go-to!) 
4. Pre-cut fruits & veggies (fresh is best!) 
5. Wholemeal flour (millets & gluten-free for the win!)

ZERO BREAKOUTS?! Here’s
Part 01: How I Cleared My Skin Naturally (PCOS-friendly!)
 No meds. No expensive products. Just real results.
After years of struggling with hormonal breakouts (hello PCOS acne), this is the longest I’ve gone WITHOUT a breakout — and I did it through FOOD.

I CUT OUT: ❌ Wheat + dairy (gut + hormone balance = magic) ❌ Ultra-processed junk ❌ Starchy carbs like pasta, white rice, white potatoes

& I ADDED IN: ✅ Green juice every morning (anti-inflammatory + detoxifying) ✅ One BIG salad daily — packed with fiber ✅ Complex carbs that support hormones (mix colour quinoa, buckwheat & sweet potatoes are some of my favourites)

This is the real acne treatment no one talks about — especially for PCOS besties.
